####################
# Test that I find all the markers in a file
####################

Given (Some text with no markers in it):
  hello
  this is in the fold
  this is outside of the fold

Execute (Remove the folds [there are none]):
  call RemoveMarkers()

Expect (Nothing changed):
  hello
  this is in the fold
  this is outside of the fold


Given (Some text with a single set of markers in it):
  first line
  {{{
  this was in a fold
  }}}
  no longer in a fold

Execute (Remove the folds):
  call RemoveMarkers()

Expect (Folds removed):
  first line
  this was in a fold
  no longer in a fold
